w! |- |13 ||Tiina: ||Hei hei! (Tiina lähtee.) ||Bye bye! (Tiina leaves) |- |14 ||Sakari: ||Siskosi on [[Wiktionary:todella#Finnish|todella]] [[Wiktionary:kaunis#Finnish|kaunis]]. [[Wiktionary:onko#Finnish|Onko]] hän [[Wiktionary:malli#Finnish|malli]]? ||Your sister is really beautiful. Is she a model? |- |15 ||Markku: ||Ei, [[Wiktionary:vaan#Finnish|vaan]] hän on toimittaja. Kaunis hän [[Wiktionary:kyllä#Finnish|kyllä]] on. ||No, she is a journalist. Though she is pretty, indeed. |- |16 ||Juha: || Markkuuu! ||Markku!! |- |17 ||Tiina: || Markku! [[Wiktionary:tule#Finnish|Tule]] jo! ||Markku, hurry up! |}
