* ____ ___ Markku? (is he Markku?) |- ! style="color: blue;background-color: white;" | * Onko hän Markku? |}
{| class="navbox collapsible collapsed" style="text-align: left; border: 1px; margin-top: 0.2em;" |- ! style="background-color: white; " | * Minä olen isä (I am a father) * ______ ____ isä? (Am I the father?) |- ! style="color: blue;background-color: white;" | * Olenko minä isä? |}
{| class="navbox collapsible collapsed" style="text-align: left; border: 1px; margin-top: 0.2em;" |- ! style="background-color: white; " | * Me olemme metroasemalla (We are on a metro station) * __________ __ metroasemalla? (Are we on the metro station?) |- ! style="color: blue;background-color: white;" | * Olemmeko me metroasemalla? |}
{| class="navbox collapsible collapsed" style="text-align: left; border: 1px; margin-top: 0.2em;" |- ! style="background-color: white; " | * Hänen siskonsa on malli (His/her sister is a model) * _____ _______ ____________ malli? (Is his sister a model?) |- ! style="color: blue;background-color: white;" | * Onko hänen siskonsa malli? |}
